hm.binkley.util.logging

Class MinimumLogger

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.slf4j.ext.LoggerWrapper
      • hm.binkley.util.logging.MinimumLogger
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Logger

    public class MinimumLogger
extends LoggerWrapper
    MinimalLogger complains about trivial logging. When a logger supports only a given level or greater, attempts to log at a lesser level throw IllegalStateException.
    Author:
    B. K. Oxley (binkley)
